---
title: Golden Breaded Shrimp with DIY Tartar Sauce and Potato Coins
description: Pub-grub and kid-friendly combine in our golden breaded shrimp! Everyone will love the zesty DIY tartar sauce paired with roasted potato coins for dunking!
